data.description: Charming Charming Charming!!!  This sweet home, located in Imperial and in the sought after Windsor School District is fully updated and ready for its new owner to love!  Sitting on .5 acre, this beauty features: Vinyl Plank Flooring throughout; Open & Spacious floorplan; 4 Bedrooms (2 bedrooms on main floor, 2 legal bedrooms in the lower level); 2 full bathrooms; fully finished, walk-out lower level; ENORMOUS, fully fenced, rear yard! No HOA! You'll be impressed with the generous size of the bedrooms! The roof is only 4 years old, HVAC System only 3 years old!! You'll be excited to make this gem your new home! Showings begin Saturday, 11/25/23!!
